CALIFORNIA GOVERNOR FAVORS FINANCING INTEREST IN UTILITIES
Gov. Gray Davis on Friday threw his weight behind a controversial plan to 
have the state provide financial relief to Southern California Edison and 
Pacific Gas & Electric in return for partial ownership of the debt-wracked 
utilities.
