dder/2001/01/29/krtbn/0000-0077-OC-POWER-CRISIS

PSEG, PANDA JV'S 1,000-MW TEXAS POWER PLANT ON LINE
A 1,000-megawatt power plant in Guadelupe, Texas has begun commercial 
operations, its owners said Monday.
